snippet.title: Slaughter Me Street 1999 | All Levels On Slaughter Difficulty (No Deaths Kinda)
snippet.description:
I honestly had a blast playing this, even though its frustrating. I still enjoy it regardless, worth the 5 bucks on steam!


The reason why the title has the "No Deaths Kinda" is because i died before my winning run, which is why it shows How much deaths you died on that level. Can't refresh it for some reason soooooo.


also its my birthday :p
